==English==

===Etymology===
Sometimes claimed to be from Indian vernacular for ''[[fuck]]'', though no confirmation has been found
===Noun===
'''choad'''
#{{slang}} a general [[insult]], referring to someone as a [[loser]], etc.
#{{slang}} a short, but wide [[penis]] giving the appearance that it is nearly [[flat]].
#{{slang}} a general term used to desrcribe the area  of skin between the bottom of a mans scrotum and the anus.

